28
00:02:41,448 --> 00:02:42,448
Why aren't

29
00:02:42,448 --> 00:02:43,927
their people here yet?

30
00:02:44,047 --> 00:02:45,008
Master, don't panic.

31
00:02:45,008 --> 00:02:46,288
Our sect leader sent Wu Chuan

32
00:02:46,288 --> 00:02:47,087
