34
00:02:49,207 --> 00:02:50,607
This is an urgent crisis.

35
00:02:50,607 --> 00:02:52,487
Must they bathe, change clothes,

36
00:02:52,487 --> 00:02:54,087
and burn incense before coming?

37
00:02:54,288 --> 00:02:55,807
That old fool Song He

38
00:02:55,807 --> 00:02:56,767
is utterly unreliable.

39
00:02:56,767 --> 00:02:57,848
If he doesn't come soon...

40
00:02:57,848 --> 00:02:58,448
Tan Feng.

41
00:02:58,528 --> 00:02:59,927
If they don't arrive,

42
00:02:59,927 --> 00:03:01,647
we two will find a way to storm in.

43
