Master,

44
00:03:03,487 --> 00:03:04,688
didn't we just try and fail

45
00:03:04,688 --> 00:03:06,128
before turning to Liuguang Sect?

46
00:03:06,128 --> 00:03:06,688
Right.

47
00:03:07,327 --> 00:03:10,288
Kong Hou is trapped inside.

48
00:03:10,288 --> 00:03:13,448
Can't you think of another solution?

49
00:03:13,848 --> 00:03:15,487
Tan Feng, better keep quiet.

50
00:03:15,568 --> 00:03:16,968
No matter how angry you are,

51
00:03:16,968 --> 00:03:18,128
