52
00:03:18,128 --> 00:03:19,168
Should I vent

53
00:03:19,168 --> 00:03:20,087
on you instead?

54
00:03:20,128 --> 00:03:20,968
Stop.

55
00:03:20,968 --> 00:03:22,248
Calm down.

56
00:03:22,248 --> 00:03:23,807
Just stay calm, Master Wang Tong.

57
00:03:26,767 --> 00:03:28,568
I heard there's a secluded

58
00:03:28,568 --> 00:03:30,128
cultivation spot ahead

59
00:03:30,128 --> 00:03:31,128
full of spiritual energy.

60
00:03:31,248 --> 00:03:32,288
Our sect

61
00:03:32,288 --> 00:03:33,848
has specifically prepared it

62
00:03:33,848 --> 00:03:35,728
for high-level disciples'
cultivation needs.

63
00:03:36,087 --> 00:03:37,087
Hold on.

64
00:03:37,087 --> 00:03:38,128
We're almost there.

65
00:03:38,767 --> 00:03:39,647
Maybe wait here

66
00:03:39,647 --> 00:03:40,487
for a moment?

67
00:03:40,487 --> 00:03:41,047
Come on.

68
00:03:41,647 --> 00:03:42,688
Be careful.

69
00:04:13,767 --> 00:04:14,248
Come on.

70
00:04:17,127 --> 00:04:17,968
