71
00:04:20,408 --> 00:04:21,208
Slowly.

72
00:04:24,208 --> 00:04:25,127
Hold on.

73
00:04:25,848 --> 00:04:26,968
Almost there.

74
00:04:27,807 --> 00:04:28,367
Come on.

75
00:04:37,367 --> 00:04:39,007
This is the place. Hang in there.

76
00:04:39,007 --> 00:04:39,927
You will be fine.

77
00:04:39,927 --> 00:04:41,247
I'll get Master to help you.

78
00:04:41,247 --> 00:04:41,927
Wait for me.

79
00:04:46,127 --> 00:04:47,247
There's no time.

80
00:04:47,888 --> 00:04:48,768
You do it.

81
00:04:48,927 --> 00:04:49,807
Me?

82
00:04:49,927 --> 00:04:51,367
