95
00:06:53,927 --> 00:06:55,127
is truly exhausting work.

96
00:06:55,247 --> 00:06:56,687
I actually fell asleep.

97
00:06:59,768 --> 00:07:01,088
Your complexion looks healthy,

98
00:07:01,088 --> 00:07:02,208
your energy is robust,

99
00:07:02,208 --> 00:07:04,088
and your wound has healed.

100
00:07:10,168 --> 00:07:12,447
