101
00:07:12,528 --> 00:07:13,888
Don't mention it.

102
00:07:13,888 --> 00:07:14,728
Hadn't you helped

103
00:07:14,728 --> 00:07:15,927
absorb so much spiritual...

104
00:07:19,047 --> 00:07:20,088
Never mind.

105
00:07:20,888 --> 00:07:21,888
I mean,

106
00:07:21,888 --> 00:07:23,247
your wound did heal completely.

107
00:07:23,247 --> 00:07:24,168
This place

108
00:07:24,168 --> 00:07:25,247
is our Yunhua Sect's

109
00:07:25,247 --> 00:07:26,528
treasured cultivation site.

110
00:07:26,528 --> 00:07:28,208
It's truly extraordinary.

111
00:07:28,968 --> 00:07:30,247
If you're alright,

112
00:07:30,367 --> 00:07:31,328
let's leave now.

113
00:07:31,487 --> 00:07:31,968
Okay.

114
00:07:45,687 --> 00:07:46,528
What are you doing?

115
00:07:46,648 --> 00:07:48,648
I'm so awesome now.

116
00:07:48,768 --> 00:07:50,247
What's so awesome about that?

117
00:07:50,328 --> 00:07:51,447
(If he can help me)

118
00:07:51,447 --> 00:07:52,567
(get more spiritual energy,)

119
00:07:52,687 --> 00:07:53,728
(maybe I'll qualify)

120
00:07:53,728 --> 00:07:54,888
(to choose a spiritual tool.)

121
00:07:56,487 --> 00:07:57,247
By the way,

122
00:07:57,567 --> 00:07:58,687
at the very least,

123
00:07:58,687 --> 00:08:00,168
I did save your life.

124
00:08:00,168 --> 00:08:01,888
And all I get is a 'thank you'?

125
00:08:02,288 --> 00:08:04,168
I never leave debts unpaid.

126
00:08:04,288 --> 00:08:05,247
What do you want?

127
00:08:06,728 --> 00:08:07,927
You'd give me

128
00:08:07,927 --> 00:08:09,007
whatever I want?

129
00:08:09,007 --> 00:08:09,728
Name it.

130
00:08:13,288 --> 00:08:14,768
What are you doing now?

131
00:08:15,408 --> 00:08:17,047
Didn't you say you'd give me

132
00:08:17,047 --> 00:08:18,247
whatever I want?

133
00:08:18,447 --> 00:08:20,007
I just want to hold your hand.

134
00:08:20,007 --> 00:08:20,888
Come with me.

135
00:08:21,567 --> 00:08:22,968
Let go.

136
00:08:23,288 --> 00:08:24,528
Low in spiritual energy,

137
00:08:24,528 --> 00:08:25,487
mighty in strength?

138
00:08:25,487 --> 00:08:26,768
What exactly do you want?

139
00:08:26,768 --> 00:08:27,728
Let's go.

140
00:08:27,888 --> 00:08:29,288
Haven't I already explained?

141
00:08:29,288 --> 00:08:29,968
I'm scared.

142
00:08:29,968 --> 00:08:31,607
Holding onto you makes me feel safer.

143
00:08:31,607 --> 00:08:32,327
Stop.

144
00:08:34,087 --> 00:08:35,047
Let me go.

145
00:08:35,047 --> 00:08:35,648
I...

146
00:08:37,528 --> 00:08:38,488
Fine.

147
00:08:38,488 --> 00:08:40,047
I won't touch you.

148
00:08:40,248 --> 00:08:41,807
In that case,

149
00:08:41,807 --> 00:08:45,488
does your earlier promise still stand?

150
00:08:47,648 --> 00:08:49,248
As long as it's not this absurd,

151
00:08:49,248 --> 00:08:50,368
I'll agree to anything.

152
00:08:50,648 --> 00:08:52,168
That works too.

153
00:08:52,288 --> 00:08:53,128
However,

154
00:08:53,128 --> 00:08:55,488
I'll need to save my request for later.

155
00:08:55,488 --> 00:08:56,768
Because I haven't decided yet

156
00:08:56,768 --> 00:08:58,128
what exactly to ask from you.

157
00:08:58,727 --> 00:09:00,288
Storybooks say

158
00:09:00,288 --> 00:09:02,087
that your Luanfeng Peak's ranks

159
00:09:02,087 --> 00:09:04,408
contain little gold cultivators,
silver cultivators,

160
00:09:04,408 --> 00:09:05,368
and bronze cultivators.

161
00:09:05,847 --> 00:09:07,648
You seem quite skilled.

162
00:09:07,648 --> 00:09:08,727
What's your rank?

163
00:09:08,727 --> 00:09:10,608
Are you a little silver cultivator?

164
00:09:10,807 --> 00:09:11,847
Let me make this clear.

165
00:09:12,047 --> 00:09:12,927
We don't have

166
00:09:12,927 --> 00:09:14,087
the ranks you mentioned.

167
00:09:14,207 --> 00:09:15,648
Nor do we have

168
00:09:16,047 --> 00:09:17,888
gold, silver, or bronze cultivators.

169
00:09:18,008 --> 00:09:20,327
They're 'little gold,' 'little silver,'

170
00:09:20,327 --> 00:09:21,807
and 'little bronze' cultivators.

171
00:09:25,608 --> 00:09:27,408
So those were all lies?

172
00:09:27,488 --> 00:09:28,567
Still, those titles

173
00:09:28,567 --> 00:09:29,967
do sound rather imposing.

174
00:09:30,687 --> 00:09:31,847
Consider using them.

175
00:09:31,847 --> 00:09:32,888
It's never too late.

176
00:09:32,888 --> 00:09:33,608
No need.

177
00:09:35,447 --> 00:09:36,288
We're here.

178
00:09:36,488 --> 00:09:37,567
Finally.

179
00:09:44,768 --> 00:09:46,888
This barrier is a formation.

180
00:09:46,927 --> 00:09:47,488
I...

181
00:09:48,807 --> 00:09:49,927
I'm injured.

182
00:09:49,927 --> 00:09:50,847
I can't channel energy.

183
00:09:51,008 --> 00:09:52,528
But I can't do this.

184
00:09:52,888 --> 00:09:54,207
Follow my instructions.

185
00:09:56,608 --> 00:09:57,528
Fine.

186
00:09:57,687 --> 00:09:59,584
- Now chant the incantation
- Nature, one with all.

187
00:09:59,584 --> 00:10:01,168
- and channel all your spiritual energy.
- In the void, truths unfold.

188
00:10:01,168 --> 00:10:02,687
Eight directions' divine might

189
00:10:02,687 --> 00:10:04,128
guides me to harmony.

190
00:10:04,248 --> 00:10:05,567
The Primordial King's decree

191
00:10:05,648 --> 00:10:07,687
is heard by the Nine Heavens.

192
00:10:14,727 --> 00:10:15,927
Focus.

193
00:10:16,648 --> 00:10:18,727
Let your spiritual energy
follow the incantation

194
00:10:18,888 --> 00:10:20,368
to flow through all your meridians.

195
00:10:38,816 --> 00:10:39,904
Master Wang Tong. Tan Feng.

196
00:10:39,904 --> 00:10:40,928
Look. The barrier's open.

197
00:10:40,928 --> 00:10:42,248
Master, it's open.

198
00:10:43,648 --> 00:10:44,447
Since it's open,

199
00:10:44,447 --> 00:10:45,528
why aren't we rushing in?

200
00:10:45,528 --> 00:10:46,168
Okay.

201
00:10:46,967 --> 00:10:47,807
You know what?

202
00:10:47,807 --> 00:10:48,648
Our Yunhua Sect

203
00:10:48,648 --> 00:10:49,888
has endless treats and marvels

204
00:10:49,888 --> 00:10:51,168
you've never experienced.

205
00:10:51,327 --> 00:10:52,528
Since you're here,

206
00:10:52,528 --> 00:10:53,567
why not stay

207
00:10:53,567 --> 00:10:54,687
for a few more days

208
00:10:54,687 --> 00:10:56,047
before returning to Liuguang Sect?

209
00:10:56,047 --> 00:10:56,528
Deal?

210
00:10:56,608 --> 00:10:57,288
No need.

211
00:10:58,847 --> 00:11:01,488
Don't be polite with me.

212
00:11:01,488 --> 00:11:02,967
Just stay at Yunhua Sect

213
00:11:02,967 --> 00:11:03,888
for a few more days

214
00:11:03,967 --> 00:11:05,687
and tell all my fellow disciples

215
00:11:05,687 --> 00:11:07,087
of my deeds of courage

216
00:11:07,087 --> 00:11:08,168
and unshaken resolve

217
00:11:08,168 --> 00:11:09,047
in crisis.

218
00:11:09,047 --> 00:11:10,807
If it comes from your mouth,

219
00:11:10,807 --> 00:11:12,648
they'll definitely believe every word.

220
00:11:12,648 --> 00:11:13,567
You can stop here.

221
00:11:14,368 --> 00:11:16,408
Won't you stay for tea?

222
00:11:17,368 --> 00:11:18,847
No need. Thank you.

223
00:11:20,288 --> 00:11:23,768
Will we meet again?

224
00:11:23,768 --> 00:11:25,408
Danger always follows me.

225
00:11:25,608 --> 00:11:26,888
We shouldn't meet again.

226
00:11:27,727 --> 00:11:29,760
But you must rest sometime.

227
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,200
Let's meet during your rest periods.

228
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:31,872
Problem solved.

229
00:11:31,872 --> 00:11:33,327
I never rest.

230
00:11:34,168 --> 00:11:37,047
You're terrible at conversation.

231
00:11:40,248 --> 00:11:41,648
What's your name?

232
00:11:42,807 --> 00:11:44,888
Kong Hou. My name is Kong Hou.

233
00:11:48,927 --> 00:11:49,567
Noted.

234
00:11:51,648 --> 00:11:52,687
Goodbye.

235
00:11:52,888 --> 00:11:54,447
We must meet again.

236
00:11:54,608 --> 00:11:55,967
Kong Hou?

237
00:11:55,967 --> 00:11:57,488
- Kong Hou?
- Kong Hou?

238
00:11:58,927 --> 00:12:00,447
- Kong Hou?
- Kong Hou?

239
00:12:00,528 --> 00:12:01,567
Kong Hou?

240
00:12:02,368 --> 00:12:05,047
Kong Hou? Kong Hou?

241
00:12:05,528 --> 00:12:07,047
Kong Hou?

242
00:12:08,768 --> 00:12:10,128
- Kong Hou?
- Kong Hou?

243
00:12:10,128 --> 00:12:10,888
Master.

244
00:12:10,888 --> 00:12:12,248
Tan Feng. Ling Hui.

245
00:12:12,248 --> 00:12:13,168
Kong Hou.

246
00:12:17,207 --> 00:12:18,567
Excellent.

247
00:12:18,567 --> 00:12:19,967
All limbs intact.

248
00:12:19,967 --> 00:12:21,248
Not a single part missing.

249
00:12:21,248 --> 00:12:23,327
Truly uninjured anywhere?

250
00:12:23,967 --> 00:12:24,967
Master,

251
00:12:25,008 --> 00:12:26,087
I'm fine.

252
00:12:26,087 --> 00:12:27,768
Good that you're safe.

253
00:12:27,768 --> 00:12:29,408
You reckless girl!

254
00:12:29,408 --> 00:12:31,207
Trying to scare me to death?

255
00:12:31,207 --> 00:12:32,128
Did you want to die?

256
00:12:32,128 --> 00:12:34,128
Why meddle in unnecessary business

257
00:12:34,128 --> 00:12:36,008
and come to the Forbidden Forest?

258
00:12:36,488 --> 00:12:38,528
Master, I was wrong.

259
00:12:38,528 --> 00:12:40,207
I came for serious reasons.

260
00:12:40,687 --> 00:12:42,488
Apologizing isn't enough.

261
00:12:42,488 --> 00:12:43,207
All these years,

262
00:12:43,207 --> 00:12:45,168
you've caused me so much trouble.

263
00:12:45,168 --> 00:12:46,567
Today I'll properly

264
00:12:46,567 --> 00:12:47,408
punish you.

265
00:12:47,408 --> 00:12:48,847
I'll punish you

266
00:12:49,128 --> 00:12:50,727
to copy all the cultivation techniques

267
00:12:50,727 --> 00:12:51,768
from the past three months

268
00:12:51,768 --> 00:12:53,727
ten thousand... No, one thousand...

269
00:12:53,727 --> 00:12:54,888
One hundred times!

270
00:12:55,327 --> 00:12:56,807
Master,

271
00:12:56,927 --> 00:12:59,168
three months' worth of techniques

272
00:12:59,207 --> 00:13:01,288
is a massive stack.

273
00:13:01,288 --> 00:13:02,648
Copying them a hundred times?

274
00:13:02,648 --> 00:13:04,368
I'll die from exhaustion.

275
00:13:04,447 --> 00:13:05,727
Exactly, Master Wang Tong.

276
00:13:05,727 --> 00:13:07,648
How's that even possible?

277
00:13:08,927 --> 00:13:10,648
What are you two doing?

278
00:13:10,768 --> 00:13:11,368
Back then,

279
00:13:11,368 --> 00:13:12,567
when I got punished,

280
00:13:12,727 --> 00:13:14,488
I never complained.

281
00:13:14,488 --> 00:13:16,047
You didn't complain

282
00:13:16,168 --> 00:13:18,128
because you'd run away immediately.

283
00:13:18,128 --> 00:13:19,648
Now that Kong Hou's in trouble,

284
00:13:19,648 --> 00:13:21,207
you're not helping her.

285
00:13:21,207 --> 00:13:21,967
Instead, you're

286
00:13:21,967 --> 00:13:24,087
- making it worse.
- Master.

287
00:13:24,087 --> 00:13:24,847
No, Master. Stop.

288
00:13:24,927 --> 00:13:25,608
Stop there.

289
00:13:25,608 --> 00:13:26,967
Punish her, not me.

290
00:13:26,967 --> 00:13:27,727
Master. Master.

291
00:13:27,727 --> 00:13:29,168
